org.kaaproject.kaa.client.channel

Interface KaaDataMultiplexer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBootstrapDataProcessor, DefaultOperationDataProcessor

    public interface KaaDataMultiplexer
    Multiplexer collects the info about states from different services and compiles it in one request. Required in user implementation of any kind of data channel.
    Author:
    Yaroslav Zeygerman
